{
  "stem": "2684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and they-- With me, another 40 or 50 young guys, a few of them friend of mine, a few of them from the orphanage of Budapest, they established a, a, a tiny little commando.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we went out a place called Nagyteteny, which is about 15, 18 kilometers from Budapest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were employed by the Hungarian Road Building Ministerium, the road department here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And our job was, they give us-- they took us from the [NON-ENGLISH] by truck out to the site.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we had to shovel the roads.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had to dig out the roads.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then they put stones on it, and then we had to level the stones and then put sand on it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we were working actually as, as road builders.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we went there in the morning and came home in the night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And to me, that was beautiful, because I was out from, from the, from the allocated area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I could move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when the bombardment came to Budapest, from Nagyteteny, we could see the planes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We could hear the air raids, the sirens.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We could see the planes coming because we were up in the-- in the little mountainous area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And as youngsters, we watched the planes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We didn't know the significance so much of the bombing, although we'd been under the buildings in the last three, four years quite many times when the air raid signal came.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But that was-- everybody had to go down, because the bomb didn't discriminate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And so we watched with child eyes how the Americans and the Englishmen bombarded Budapest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So when, when this happened, after the bombardments, they stopped us going into the, the road work.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
